Money Stuff =0A One model is that some trades want to be done with a lot of=
 leverage. Here=E2=80=99s =0Aone: I buy a $1 million Treasury bond. I sell =
you a $1 million =0A=0A=0A <> =0A =0A<https://sli.bloomberg.com/click=3Fs=
=3D825881&stpe=3Ddefault&li=3D12724789&m=3D21d6dea82d6b16615cf44233be620525=
&p=3D02252025>=0A=0A=0A=0APeople are worried about the basis trade=0A=0AOne=
 model is that some trades want to be done with a lot of leverage. Here=E2=
=80=99s =0Aone:=0A=0A * I buy a $1 million Treasury bond. =0A * I sell you =
