om-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; ba=
ckground-color: #ccc;">One is</a>: I do it =E2=80=9Cto exploit price discre=
pancies in government-bond markets.=E2=80=9D Both parts of the trade =E2=80=
=94=C2=A0the Treasury bond and the Treasury future =E2=80=94=C2=A0trade on =
