ome leverage by selling you the futures.)</p> <p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=
Both of these answers are important, though. The first answer =E2=80=94=C2=
=A0I do the trade to profit from price discrepancies =E2=80=94=C2=A0describ=
es my motivation; it describes me as a=C2=A0<em>proprietary trader</em>, do=
ing the trade to extract money for myself from the workings of the financia=
l markets. The second answer =E2=80=94=C2=A0I do the trade to provide you w=
ith the futures you want =E2=80=94=C2=A0describes my economic function; it =
